<div style="text-align: left;">

## Pratiques DevOps

- Agilité, Scrum
- Automation, CI/CD
- Microservices
- Infra as Code
- Monitoring, Observability
- Alerting
- DevSecOps, ShiftLeft
- GitOps

</div>
